Their servant guides the carrier to death, he can practice the warrior standing in front of him by controlling and moving the target to different sides and ranges.
It should be emphasized that in recent years, Border Police fighters have dealt with many terror attacks, in which the assailant shoots and poses a threat while moving in arenas saturated with innocent civilians.
The "Assaf Facility", in its current version, is based on components and parts that are used in various fields.
For example, the telescopic rod that was upgraded and integrated into the facility was taken from the field of maintenance and cleaning.
Using the device, it is possible to simulate shooting in motion within a civilian population towards a dynamic target while maintaining eye contact with the object, handling traffic impairments, choosing a path of progress, selective firing, including practicing preventing harm to non-combatants.
